    "description": "<br><br>欢迎来到Retro Drive宇宙 - 一个80年代精神以霓虹辉光闪耀的天堂。冲进一个霓虹灯和脉动节拍的时间旅行漩涡。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142380/extras/3e47b3fa0a15f4bca4a027e3f64c4327.poster.avif?t=1750088605\" width=640 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142380/extras/3e47b3fa0a15f4bca4a027e3f64c4327.webm?t=1750088605\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142380/extras/3e47b3fa0a15f4bca4a027e3f64c4327.mp4?t=1750088605\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142380/extras/824601656c6ec91cb973d949fa2ea95e.avif?t=1750088605\" width=640 height=90 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >欢迎来到复古城</h2>征服复古城的活力街道。无论是与时间赛跑还是躲避警察，你的技能都会受到考验。调高音量，踩下油门，追上你的朋友们！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142380/extras/1b33db944aaf98d13b69914048800b75.poster.avif?t=1750088605\" width=640 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142380/extras/1b33db944aaf98d13b69914048800b75.webm?t=1750088605\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142380/extras/1b33db944aaf98d13b69914048800b75.mp4?t=1750088605\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142380/extras/81dab57133d0c0041d14b13c157c984f.avif?t=1750088605\" width=640 height=90 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >激进的汽车</h2>在比赛中积累积分以解锁各种可定制的汽车。你的座驾越酷，你在复古城中疾驰的速度就越快。在霓虹灯照耀的街道上风驰电掣吧！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142380/extras/d92d07740e49a4de495cadce24b08b44.poster.avif?t=1750088605\" width=640 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142380/extras/d92d07740e49a4de495cadce24b08b44.webm?t=1750088605\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142380/extras/d92d07740e49a4de495cadce24b08b44.mp4?t=1750088605\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142380/extras/6e6c52b30f2431f46ee01b5e9e2e22a8.avif?t=1750088605\" width=640 height=90 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >合成波传奇</h2>沉浸在合成波的世界中，伴随着令人难忘的原声音乐，艺术家包括：<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>New Arcades<br></li><li>Neon Nox<br></li><li>Fantom '87<br></li><li>Michael Oakley<br></li><li>Sunglasses Kid<br></li><li>以及更多</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142380/extras/97c0fe6ee27a774108781f5ff98f6751.poster.avif?t=1750088605\" width=640 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142380/extras/97c0fe6ee27a774108781f5ff98f6751.webm?t=1750088605\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142380/extras/97c0fe6ee27a774108781f5ff98f6751.mp4?t=1750088605\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142380/extras/b789ddcea69bde1cde17ae15f22ec2be.avif?t=1750088605\" width=620 height=620 /></span>",
